1. On *puši* cigaretu na terasi. (He is *smoking* a cigarette on the terrace.)
2. U ovoj prostoriji nije dozvoljeno *pušenje*. (*Smoking* is not allowed in this room.)
3. Da li ti *pušiš*? (Do you *smoke*?)
4. Oni *puše* u tim prostorijama već godinama. (They have been *smoking* in those rooms for years.)
5. Pogledaj tu veliku fabriku dima, tamo neko *puši*. (Look at that huge smokestack, someone is *smoking* there.)
6. Zbog zdravlja, odlučio sam da prestanem da *pušim*. (For my health, I have decided to quit *smoking*.)
7. *Pušiš* previše, moraš da smanjiš. (You *smoke* too much, you need to cut down.)
8. Nije u redu što on *puši* u prisustvu dece. (It's not okay for him to *smoke* in front of children.)
9. Čuo sam da je taj restoran poznat po dobroj hrani i da se tamo može *pušiti*. (I heard that restaurant is famous for its good food and that you can *smoke* there.)
10. Našao sam staru fotografiju svog dede kako *puši* lulu. (I found an old photograph of my grandfather *smoking* a pipe.)